title: Straame Laundry and Storage Bag, Multipurpose Storage Bag, Durable and Resistant Storage Solution with Zips and Handles, Large Reusable Bags (60 x 60 Pack of 5)
features: CONVENIENT & MULTI-PURPOSE: Straame’s sturdy, strong, and spacious storage bags are perfect for moving or storing and make a lightweight, economical alternative to moving boxes. Our bags provide maximum convenience without any extra packing supplies needed. You can store everything from clothes to toys and household items. Our zipped laundry bags are ideal for space-saving, room organization, storage, moving, camping, traveling, and more.

HEAVY-DUTY & DURABLE: The bags are reinforced with extra stitching on all carrying handles that wrap around the bag for maximum strength and security. The bags are designed for heavier loading and can safely hold up more weight. These bags are made from our premium polypropylene woven material that is easy to clean with wipes, easy to maintain, and Weather-resistant. They are an excellent alternative for moving houses or as an extra-large grocery shopping bag.

FOLDABLE & REUSABLE: Straame moving bags can be easily folded into a compact size and can be stored in a closet, car, in a drawer, or in luggage without occupying more space. Which eliminates the difficulty of assembling or disassembling boxes. They can be folded flat when not in use, taking up minimal space. The bags can be reused for your future needs with our economical design and sustainability in mind.

VINTAGE DESIGN FOR STORAGE: Straame multipurpose storage bags are the solution to your storage problems. A classic and traditional design to easily recognize and spot your belongings. Keep your items organized while still moving in style. Whether you need to collect your laundry, a place for your seasonal clothes/bedding/blankets, or you need a large bag to put away all your Christmas decorations; these large bags are the right choice for you.

PRODUCT DETAILS: Perfect to store bulky items, winter duvets, or seasonal decorations. Straame storage bags with zip measures 60cm x 60cm x 18cm and 80cm x 60cm x 28cm and are available in pack of 5 and 10. Colours assorted.
